<div class="title">Way Worse Than Drunk Dialing</div>
<div class="substance">Clonazepam (Klonopin) & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Anonymous+&Exact=1">Anonymous </a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Anonymous . "Way Worse Than Drunk Dialing: An Experience with Clonazepam (Klonopin) & Alcohol (exp69540)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 24, 2009. erowid.org/exp/69540</div>

<br/>



